==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: chóurén xiāng jiàn, fēnwài yănhóng
===Proverb===
'''[[仇人]][[相]][[見]]，[[分外]][[眼紅]]'''
# when two enemies meet, their eyes are especially red; When enemies come face to face, their eyes blaze with hate.
===Alternate forms===
[[仇人相见，分外眼红]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
